### Hadith 2:65

*Narrated Nafi':*

Ibn Umar said something similar to Mujahid's saying: Whenever (Muslims
and non-Muslims) stand face to face in battle, the Muslims can pray
while standing. Ibn Umar added, "The Prophet said, 'If the number of the
enemy is greater than the Muslims, they can pray while standing or
riding (individually).' "

